divs: Sighting DetailsOn August 15th 2005, I went outside to go take out the trash. I was going back inside when I saw a white metallic speck right over my head. my first impression was that it was just an airline jet at a high altitude, but it was moving way to slow. then it just stopped there. suddenly, it started moving again. I thought that was kinda strange so I got inside and got my digital camera and proceded outside to take a picture of it. The object was oval shaped and was moving towards the south. I took two pictures of it and then it just faded out and disappeared as if it evaporated.
